WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.552 --> 00:00:11.386
Hi, my name is Brandon, and I have had an experience with the Lord that he keeps telling me I need to tell people about.

00:00:11.760 --> 00:00:27.188
I've never really talked in front of a camera before like this, but he wanted me to document it and tell everybody what happened and what kind of experience I had with him.

00:00:27.554 --> 00:00:40.194
This experience lasted all night long, and I'm just asking the Holy Spirit right now to help me communicate everything that I saw.

00:00:41.093 --> 00:00:47.783
It's really important because Jesus Christ is coming, and he told me he's coming face to face.

00:00:49.702 --> 00:00:59.421
This experience happened on July 6th, 2014, and I've held it all these years.

00:00:59.421 --> 00:01:06.640
I wrote it down on paper and released it to some people on Facebook and to some church friends and family.

00:01:09.530 --> 00:01:19.244
Some people received it and some people didn't. I'm just a deliverer of the message that he gave me.

00:01:19.244 --> 00:01:32.540
I'm not here to argue about theology or try to convince anybody of my experience.

00:01:33.140 --> 00:01:42.506
I'm going to tell you exactly what happened, exactly how it happened, from the beginning to the end.

00:01:43.544 --> 00:01:51.240
I don't know if you're a mid-tribulation, post-tribulation, or pre-tribulation believer.

00:01:55.827 --> 00:02:06.159
Like I said, I'm not here to argue or try to get you to say anything in the comments about what I saw or what I experienced.

00:02:06.159 --> 00:02:20.571
I'm just telling you what I saw and we'll go from there. It all started out while I was asleep; I went to bed a normal night, nothing different.

00:02:20.571 --> 00:02:27.984
I went to sleep and in the middle of my sleep, all of a sudden, I don't know if I was in my body or out of my body.

00:02:29.856 --> 00:02:42.879
I don't know how it happened; all I know is all of a sudden I was standing with Jesus, and he was on my right hand the whole time in this experience.

00:02:42.879 --> 00:02:58.024
He grabbed a hold of my hand and I'll go from there. The first scene, per se, of what I saw was Jesus standing on my right hand.

00:02:58.024 --> 00:03:09.120
He had a hold of my hand and we were in a town. I don't know what town we were in, but I know that there was a big white building over to the side.

00:03:10.719 --> 00:03:18.530
I was looking up at this big white building and at the sky, and the sky was alive.

00:03:18.530 --> 00:03:27.539
It was like it was moving; it was full of lightning and very spooky looking.

00:03:28.699 --> 00:03:37.813
I looked out over the horizon and there was this lady running towards me, and she started screaming.

00:03:37.813 --> 00:03:41.680
They were all screaming in terror; they were all freaking out.

00:03:41.680 --> 00:03:48.720
It was incredible. They were saying, "They're gone. They're gone.

00:03:50.023 --> 00:03:57.297
" I said, "Who's gone? " I told this lady, "Who's gone? " and she said, "Did you not see?

00:03:57.546 --> 00:04:04.630
" I said, "Did I not see what, ma'am? What are you talking about? " At this time, she could see me.

00:04:04.630 --> 00:04:12.427
Now, not every time in this experience were people able to see me.

00:04:12.738 --> 00:04:19.172
In this instance, she could not see Jesus, but she could see me.

00:04:19.519 --> 00:04:25.647
She said, "The aliens? The aliens came and got the Christians.

00:04:26.213 --> 00:04:30.808
" I said, "The aliens? " She said, "Yes, they all disappeared.

00:04:30.808 --> 00:04:40.360
They went up. " At that moment, she just ran off. She was frantic, screaming in terror.

00:04:42.137 --> 00:04:47.712
She ran as fast as she could, panicking. I looked out over the horizon of the city.

00:04:47.712 --> 00:04:53.340
I was up on a hill at this time and I could see everything on fire.

00:04:53.340 --> 00:04:58.582
Everything was on fire—the cars, the houses, the buildings.

00:04:59.908 --> 00:05:07.600
It was like chaos beyond anything you could ever comprehend was happening at this time.

00:05:07.970 --> 00:05:14.432
You could smell the smoke. People were looting; they were stealing out of cars and buildings.

00:05:14.432 --> 00:05:23.320
They were trashing the city where I was. Jesus didn't say anything.

00:05:24.240 --> 00:05:29.973
In fact, he never spoke; I could perceive his thoughts when he was touching my hand.

00:05:29.973 --> 00:05:34.999
I knew what he was thinking, but he never said anything out of his mouth.

00:05:34.999 --> 00:05:41.919
He could understand what I was thinking, but I never said anything to him.

00:05:41.919 --> 00:05:47.440
I was just looking across the city, thinking, "Oh my gosh, what is going on?

00:05:47.1000 --> 00:05:54.120
" All of a sudden, we translated. We left that spot and went to another spot.

00:05:56.263 --> 00:06:01.792
He grabbed my hand—we were still holding hands—but it was like we just disappeared and came to another time.

00:06:05.800 --> 00:06:17.867
In this time frame, I was looking over Europe. I knew I was looking over Europe because I was standing back, like I was watching a movie.

00:06:17.867 --> 00:06:27.693
It was very strange. I was looking out over Europe and I saw this man in Berlin.

00:06:28.222 --> 00:06:34.026
All the world leaders were behind a table. It was a round table in Berlin.

00:06:34.026 --> 00:06:41.680
It looked like a big "" office. It was a brown table, and there were chairs all around it.

00:06:42.000 --> 00:06:57.439
All of these world leaders were behind this big table, and this man—I didn't know who he was at the time, but I'll tell you later—and all of the people were asking him for help.

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:08.640
They were asking him for a solution to all the rioting and the craziness that was going on.

00:07:09.200 --> 00:07:28.089
He was instructing them on what to do. He had all the wisdom and was very powerful in demeanor, the way he carried himself. He was wearing a gray suit, and he was a Middle Eastern man.

00:07:29.795 --> 00:07:47.703
All of a sudden, that scene was over, but the Lord at that time spoke to me about a scripture and showed me how everyone would give over their kingdoms to him within one hour.

00:07:47.703 --> 00:07:58.453
As I said, I'm not a Bible scholar or a theology major; I'm just a guy who loves Jesus and seeks Him with all my heart, and I had this experience with Him.

00:08:05.916 --> 00:08:07.392
The next scene I see is this man on TV—he's on cnn, Fox, and everywhere.

00:08:16.940 --> 00:08:26.720
He is telling all the people of the world what happened to the people who disappeared, explaining that they were rebellious, that they were taken away out of rebellion, and that they were being punished.

00:08:39.760 --> 00:08:45.460
All these people were punished—it was the Christians, and they were all being taken out.

00:08:45.790 --> 00:08:57.213
Then he explained that he was the new leader of the world. I looked out and saw how he was gradually taking power.

00:09:01.227 --> 00:09:06.792
I want to tell you what I felt; this is very important: everybody wakes up every single day with a peace they don't realize they have.

00:09:18.600 --> 00:09:34.173
They go to bed with it and wake up with it. Even the worst sinner in the world has a form of peace inside of them that they don't even realize.

00:09:34.787 --> 00:09:53.184
When the rapture happens and we're taken out, there is a void of peace like I've never felt in all of my life; it blankets the earth.

00:09:53.184 --> 00:09:59.580
I used to think that the Holy Spirit left with us because He dwells in each Christian.

00:09:59.580 --> 00:10:07.320
He dwells in us, and when we invite him into our heart, I believe that he went with us when the rapture happened.

00:10:07.320 --> 00:10:25.293
I cannot back that up biblically. I don't know. All I know is that there is no prayer covering, there is no sense of peace, there is no joy. It is absolute chaos.

00:10:25.293 --> 00:10:41.960
And this man has a sense that whenever everybody looks at him, when everybody is gazing upon him, a false sense of peace is what I want to say.

00:10:43.272 --> 00:10:56.360
He brings a peace when he is on the TV. He brings a sense of comfort that everybody wants to follow him so quickly because they are so scared and everybody is so tormented.

00:10:56.360 --> 00:11:03.223
They all turn to him so quickly out of that peace that he brings, but it is dirty.

00:11:04.325 --> 00:11:14.849
I don't know how to describe it. So he is on the TV, and he is telling everybody what happened to the Christians.

00:11:16.365 --> 00:11:26.788
Then I see people in the Iran and Iraq area over there—Pakistan, that area over there—they were rejoicing.

00:11:26.788 --> 00:11:34.820
And they were all calling out and saying the Mahdi has come. The Mahdi has come.

00:11:34.820 --> 00:11:41.262
And I don't know what that means. I have studied it now a little bit more.

00:11:42.356 --> 00:11:49.831
I don't know what I'm allowed to say about all this as far as on YouTube and what will be allowed.

00:11:49.831 --> 00:11:55.780
I don't want my video to get flagged, but they were calling it the Mahdi.

00:11:55.780 --> 00:12:03.279
They were calling him the Mahdi. And so everybody was calling him the Mahdi.

00:12:09.440 --> 00:12:15.180
And so he was himself Middle Eastern. He was a Muslim. I know this because he said he was and he had a...

00:12:15.880 --> 00:12:24.000
Okay, I won't get to that part yet. Okay, this is what happens next.

00:12:24.000 --> 00:12:34.080
I see him come on TV, and he is telling everybody to bring their Bibles into the stadiums, into these areas.

00:12:46.015 --> 00:12:46.470
He said, 'If you see a Bible, it is mandated by law that everybody brings these Bibles into these areas.

00:12:46.470 --> 00:12:57.360
' And so, it was like courthouses, places like that. They were all like police stations, things like that.

00:12:57.360 --> 00:13:02.209
He brings these Bibles in and they start stacking them up—big shelves full.

00:13:03.786 --> 00:13:06.331
There were thousands, millions of Bibles just everywhere.

00:13:06.331 --> 00:13:11.640
And everybody just willfully did it; they just brought in the Bibles.

00:13:12.180 --> 00:13:17.100
And I remember seeing them everywhere. There were stacks and stacks of Bibles everywhere.

00:13:17.100 --> 00:13:26.699
And so they would write down your name on a piece of paper of who brought the Bible and what it was or whatever.

00:13:36.427 --> 00:13:46.920
And he told everybody, 'If you want to come and check out the Bible and look at it, it is okay. ' We'll let you.

00:13:47.120 --> 00:14:06.594
It was kind of a trick, though, because whenever people came in and wrote on the paper to check out their Bible that they brought in—if they wanted to look at it again—you were marked even more so.

00:14:17.920 --> 00:14:18.080
And so it was like you were being watched. It was a surveillance state.

00:14:18.080 --> 00:14:27.116
It was really weird. It was like a library, is what I want to call it.

00:14:27.116 --> 00:14:39.160
Within a couple of months, I would say I saw a football field with piles of Bibles, probably three or four stories high.

00:14:44.560 --> 00:14:47.232
It was massive—just massive. They were all being burned. All the Bibles were burned by his order.

00:15:06.039 --> 00:15:06.426
Like I said, the gasoline was all over them. They were thrown into the fire, and it was incredible.

00:15:06.426 --> 00:15:14.133
Just massive amounts of smoke and the Bibles all burning. Then I saw these flags that he put on every single courthouse.

00:15:14.133 --> 00:15:32.409
If you had a country flag, like the United States of America or Europe, those flags were taken down and his flag was put up.

00:15:35.955 --> 00:15:42.960
It was black, green, and white, and it had these gold swords that were all in the center of it—massive swords, like a saber, is what I want to call it.

00:15:42.960 --> 00:15:55.040
It was a massive sword in the center of this thing, and each color represented a terrorist group, isis and others.

00:15:55.040 --> 00:16:17.493
I'm not going to even go there because I don't know all their names, but each was a terrorist group, and they're all being thanked for bringing in his reign because they supported this so much.

00:16:17.493 --> 00:16:27.786
After that, he puts his flag on the buildings, and then this is what happens next.

00:16:27.786 --> 00:16:36.622
I go with Jesus to this other area. In this, I see people on Fridays.

00:16:52.150 --> 00:17:00.240
Every Friday, you're required to worship him. Every Friday, they all had white outfits on.

00:17:00.240 --> 00:17:14.159
Every person in the world was required to wear a white outfit, and they had white garments on their heads.

00:17:25.520 --> 00:17:25.780
The women did. And men had white garments on their heads. They had white robes on and they were all in single file lines.

00:17:25.780 --> 00:17:33.257
Every line was perfect and they were all side by side. You were required to get on your knees and worship.

00:17:42.159 --> 00:17:44.177
I saw these massive screens—huge screens all on the side of the buildings of these courthouses. On Fridays, he would appear wherever you were.

00:17:44.177 --> 00:17:54.560
If it was America or Europe or whatever, you would go to this place of worship on Fridays and look at the screen.

00:17:54.560 --> 00:18:03.230
They would worship him at those screens and it was all over the place, but they were always in white robes.

00:18:03.230 --> 00:18:12.896
They were always in these single lines and it was in town square areas.

00:18:12.896 --> 00:18:26.280
What's really interesting is that I watch a lot of videos on YouTube of people walking tours and stuff.

00:18:27.280 --> 00:18:36.276
There's a place in Rome that I saw that it happens at. There are places in my town where I live now.

00:18:36.276 --> 00:18:49.440
There's a place here and there's a place in another town not too far from me where it's being required to worship.

00:18:49.440 --> 00:19:03.040
Very interesting stuff. So Christians left. Then it goes off of him and I see Christians that were left.

00:19:03.040 --> 00:19:18.020
Now, this is the part that gets hard, and there's probably a lot of you that will disagree with this or get angry about it, but I have to tell you what I saw.

00:19:18.020 --> 00:19:28.818
It is what it is. a lot of the grace message that was preached, people lived a compromising lifestyle. They were living like the world and they got left.

00:19:36.975 --> 00:19:42.430
There were literally thousands of Christians here that thought they were born again, thought that they were living right, and thought that they did everything right, but they didn't.

00:19:54.320 --> 00:19:54.824
They were living like the world and had an appearance of godliness.

00:19:54.824 --> 00:20:05.039
Their hearts were so far from the Lord, but they thought they were with him.

00:20:08.970 --> 00:20:19.931
They were the ones that even like the Bible talks about: 'You prophesied in my name, you cast out devils in my name, you healed the sick in my name.

00:20:19.931 --> 00:20:26.640
Depart from me; I never knew you. ' That's what happened. There were Christians everywhere.

00:20:26.640 --> 00:20:38.830
There were pastors that I saw who preached that watered-down grace message who were left here in punishment because they were preaching a lukewarm gospel.

00:20:50.906 --> 00:20:51.404
They were left here, and those people were as mad as could be.

00:20:51.404 --> 00:20:58.400
It was terrible. They were after those preachers that preached that way.

00:20:58.400 --> 00:21:05.960
They said, "You lied to us. You didn't tell us the truth. " I was standing with Jesus the whole time.

00:21:05.960 --> 00:21:15.760
He said to me, "Look at this. Watch this. Remember this. " He didn't say it, but I heard his thoughts.

00:21:15.760 --> 00:21:19.740
He said, "Watch this. Look at this. " I was gazing upon this area.

00:21:34.353 --> 00:21:34.919
I knew after all this happened I was back in time, back before the Antichrist was taking over.

00:21:34.919 --> 00:21:46.293
This is at the beginning, right after the rapture happens. The people are mad. They are very angry that they're here.

00:21:47.420 --> 00:21:54.320
The pastors and these leaders—I saw some of them, and I'll never mention their names because the Lord told me not to.

00:22:05.070 --> 00:22:05.425
I saw people that were on TV teaching the gospel on tbn and stuff like that—those Christian channels that were actually left.

00:22:05.425 --> 00:22:18.880
Some of them were—like two or three. I'm not ever going to say who they were, but I'm going to tell you that they were here.

00:22:18.880 --> 00:22:25.143
There were some folks here, and they were very angry and ready to kill them.

00:22:25.143 --> 00:22:30.773
It was awful. I saw one angry Christian lady that I know very well.

00:22:39.040 --> 00:22:40.599
I worked at a church for 13 years; I was a janitor there. She was one of the members there at the church where I was.

00:22:40.599 --> 00:22:50.834
I was looking up, and she looked up at the heavens and she flipped the Lord off.

00:22:50.834 --> 00:23:03.440
She gave the Lord the middle finger and she said some expletives, and it was very bad.

00:23:16.859 --> 00:23:17.329
I was watching them all just turn on God. They were angry, turning on people.

00:23:17.329 --> 00:23:28.160
There were groups of them that were building colonies. They started saying, "We've got to get prepared.

00:23:28.160 --> 00:23:39.039
It's fixing to get really bad. We've got to get our stuff around.

00:23:39.039 --> 00:23:45.387
We know what's happened. We know what's coming. " a lot of them did.

00:23:45.387 --> 00:23:55.147
"We've got to go to the mountains. We've got to go to places of refuge.

00:23:55.147 --> 00:24:05.268
We've got to go now because we're running out of time. This is fixing to get bad really fast.

00:24:11.952 --> 00:24:12.288
" I saw these people try to have a camaraderie. There were families that were left.

00:24:20.320 --> 00:24:20.600
And this is another thing: everybody below the age of 15 was gone.

00:24:20.600 --> 00:24:29.245
All the little children were gone. All of the younger teenagers and pre-teens were gone. They all got sucked up in the rapture.

00:24:29.245 --> 00:24:43.786
But anybody that was age of accountability and older was left if you didn't know Jesus Christ and have a relationship with him.

00:24:45.378 --> 00:24:50.746
I watched these younger people go with their families. During the tribulation, I saw children being born.

00:24:50.746 --> 00:24:55.576
This part is really hard. I watched how the Christians all got together.

00:25:05.470 --> 00:25:07.429
They all go to these mountain areas and dig massive holes in the side of the mountains.

00:25:07.429 --> 00:25:13.349
They were trying to keep warm because you couldn't stay in your house.

00:25:13.349 --> 00:25:21.324
You couldn't go into town and buy groceries because the mark of the beast is coming.

00:25:21.324 --> 00:25:32.880
I'm going to tell you about it; I saw how it happens, how the mark of the beast changes you, and how they put it in your forehead.

00:25:32.880 --> 00:25:42.400
I'll get to that—I don't want to skip around too much or make this too long as I respect people's time.

00:25:47.560 --> 00:25:50.000
The Christians try to move at night. I was staying with Jesus, and he took me to a field.

00:25:50.000 --> 00:25:59.493
All I knew was it was dark outside, and the Christians were moving from place to place at night because they couldn't move during the day without being spotted.

00:26:12.560 --> 00:26:12.880
They were trying to get to places of safety. The farmers had guns like.

00:26:12.880 --> 00:26:22.813
22S and rifles, so there were still firearms and ways of protection for farmers, but I didn't see many other people with guns.

00:26:24.982 --> 00:26:31.730
The Christians didn't have guns. I don't know why—nothing was really said about that—but I know the farmers did.

00:26:31.730 --> 00:26:39.930
I remember seeing one place where these Christians were trying to go through a pasture, and dogs barking alerted the farmer inside the house.

00:26:39.930 --> 00:26:47.147
He flipped the light on, and he had a. 22 in his hand. I know it was a. 22.

00:26:47.147 --> 00:26:52.500
He fired it and called the authorities to tell them people were moving at night.

00:26:52.500 --> 00:26:57.399
He didn't know if they were Christians, but I knew they were.

00:26:57.399 --> 00:27:05.609
Then I saw men in black armored Hummer trucks with blue, infrared-looking lights inside the back. They were all black with blacked-out windows.

00:27:05.609 --> 00:27:17.040
As they drove, the Christians tried to put cement blocks in the road to slow them down so they would have enough time to run away as fast as they could.

00:27:18.660 --> 00:27:27.707
They would try to throw things in the road to slow their approach, and they were running as fast as they could to try to get away.

00:27:27.707 --> 00:27:35.039
These men had black face masks on, like covid masks, and black hoods, and they would jump out.

00:27:37.510 --> 00:27:40.831
They had black outfits on with these vests and would jump out of these black cars with these guns.

00:27:40.831 --> 00:27:44.890
But this is what's weird: I've never seen one of these before.

00:27:44.890 --> 00:27:52.728
I've tried to find them online and I can't; I've never seen this before. It was a pulse.

00:27:57.039 --> 00:27:57.679
They took these black guns and pointed them and shot, but it wasn't a bullet.

00:28:00.533 --> 00:28:12.670
It was electric, like an electromagnetic pulse, and it just stuns you, but it didn't have any stun to it like the cords that come out like they have now.

00:28:16.009 --> 00:28:23.460
It was some kind of wave of energy that came out of these things and knocked you senseless for a couple of seconds.

00:28:23.840 --> 00:28:34.919
They didn't have to reload it; they just pointed it, and the people running fell out on the ground.

00:28:50.880 --> 00:28:51.120
They would pass out right there, and by the time they would get up, it was too late; they were held captive.

00:28:51.120 --> 00:29:06.240
These men would give them an ultimatum. I saw a woman and she had these two young children—a boy and a girl born during the Tribulation.

00:29:06.240 --> 00:29:15.783
They were probably three or four years old, maybe more. They were talking, so they were young, maybe five.

00:29:15.783 --> 00:29:26.650
They said, 'We're going to give the children the chip first, and if you don't deny your Jesus, we're going to cut your kids' heads off.

00:29:26.650 --> 00:29:33.740
We're going to cut their heads off. ' Or you could take the chip.

00:29:46.399 --> 00:29:46.826
They gave them an ultimatum. The dad said, 'No, we're not taking the mark.

00:29:46.826 --> 00:29:54.142
We will die. ' The dad said, 'We're most certainly not taking the mark.

00:29:54.142 --> 00:30:06.219
' The mother said, 'No, you can't cut my babies' heads off! ' because the man had this huge sickle, a huge sword, in his hand.

00:30:06.489 --> 00:30:17.131
He was getting ready—he had the baby's head like this—and he was getting ready to just go and slice that kid's head off right there.

00:30:17.131 --> 00:30:26.725
There was no mercy. There was no conscience about it. It was just the way it was.

00:30:28.864 --> 00:30:40.240
And the dad cried out and said, "No, you must not take the mark. " And when he said that, they cut his head off right there.

00:30:43.530 --> 00:30:52.360
And I'm talking it fell and rolled at my feet, and I could smell his blood. That's how awful it was.

00:30:52.360 --> 00:31:01.130
Jesus stood there with me the whole time, and he never made a comment about it.

00:31:01.130 --> 00:31:11.225
He just told me to look. And so I looked and I watched the woman, and she said, "I'll take the mark.

00:31:11.225 --> 00:31:22.630
I'll take it. I'll take the chip. Don't take their heads. " And this is what is so incredible; it's absolutely amazing about this part.

00:31:23.790 --> 00:31:32.160
They take this chip, and instantaneously those children were crying because they just saw their dad die right in front of them.

00:31:35.515 --> 00:31:45.644
And the mom is crying and she's bawling her eyes out because she saw her husband die right in front of her.

00:31:48.613 --> 00:31:53.080
And the moment she takes the chip, the baby, the two children, and her instantaneously lose emotion.

00:31:53.080 --> 00:31:59.635
They don't have any emotion on their face. They totally lose the crying.

00:31:59.635 --> 00:32:09.977
It's like they went like a zombie right there in front of me. Their minds and everything had a peace again.

00:32:09.977 --> 00:32:23.633
It's like the chip sent a peace to their brain somehow. I don't know how; all I know is the chip did something to them and it made them calm.

00:32:23.633 --> 00:32:31.720
